===吉祥物===
粉红点的吉祥物名为“Pinkie”（小指），是个粉红色的圆形物品<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pinkdot.sg/make-your-own-pink-dot/ |title=Make Your Own Pink Dot |accessdate=2016-10-06 |archive-date=2016-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006171609/http://pinkdot.sg/make-your-own-pink-dot/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/singapore-fashion-pink-dot-collection/#gs.qAsViWU Singapore fashion store launches Pink Dot capsule collection] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/singapore-fashion-pink-dot-collection/#gs.qAsViWU |date=20161006145510 }}, Gay Star News, 5 May 2016.</ref>。

===系列活动视频===
粉红点所推出的系列视频，可说是极具影响力，历届视频多年来由当地著名电影制作人[[巫俊锋|巫俊锋]]（Boo Junfeng）制作，据报道他同时也是粉红点主办方的委员之一<ref name="change">[http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/how-can-pink-dot-change-society071212/#gs.2U6dcls How can a pink dot change society?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/how-can-pink-dot-change-society071212/#gs.2U6dcls |date=20161006150836 }}, Gay Star News, 7 December 2012.</ref>。2011年为第三届粉红点，主办方推出的活动视频就有多达20万人观看<ref name="change"/>。

